incident.description: Vehicle legally parked in a market parking space was struck on the front end and driver's side by a gray pickup truck attempting to park beside it. The other driver failed to judge distance and collided, causing significant damage. The other driver waited for police.
incident.location: Parking Lot, 2325 Main Street, Springfield, OH 45503
